title: BRIEF-‍Moviepass Says Agreement With Landmark Theatres​
text: March 27, 2018 / 1:08 PM / Updated 12 minutes ago BRIEF-‍Moviepass Says Agreement With Landmark Theatres​ Reuters Staff March 27 (Reuters) - Helios And Matheson Analytics Inc : * ‍MOVIEPASS SAYS AGREEMENT WITH LANDMARK THEATRES​ * ‍MOVIEPASS SAYS THROUGH AGREEMENT, MOVIEPASS WILL BE INTEGRATED INTO LANDMARK THEATRES’ TICKETING SYSTEM​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Reuters.Brief@thomsonreuters.com)
